{"tid":1638143,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［重要］近期有扮連登既內容農場，可能會偷瀏覽資料","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T02:47:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc9f779cce2f28772ac0902a22b67f6b3e0aac0","tid":1638143,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:19:29.000Z","msg":"世澤：<br />\n近排有好多人，share乜嘢news-lihkg、backup-lihkg果啲怪link嘅新聞，我一般唔開，因為我估到唔慌好嘢，但太多人share，呢啲 內容農場 我終於有啲少少時間check，果啲都係同一檔壹A新聞嘅垃圾website有關，好大機會係啲中國人開嘅。<br />\n<br />\n內容農場 check Source Code就知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPoKNfn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPoKNfn.jpg&h=3a58363f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲仆街website令我起極大疑心，因為佢哋係會跳去另一個domain嘅website，好明顯係一個誤導website，所以我有興趣睇個website嘅Source，一睇佢個Adsense ID，再用Google搵，我諗你嘅瀏覽資料，已經落咗入中國人手上都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n佢裡面有個 Adsense ID，係用 ca-pub-0555033727456885 ，點解會出現殘體字嘅website，所以大家應該估到佢係大榴槤，一個由喺新加坡嘅中國人開嘅惡劣website，大家應該知道，有唔少中國人，不單攞咗你嘅瀏覽資料，仲要賺咗唔少Adsense嘅廣告錢。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲內容農場，都有一個特色，如果你留意呢啲特色，根本係唔會咁容易中計：<br />\n<br />\n好多用埋啲奇怪domain name，Domain Name Authority超差<br />\n佢哋好多嘢 Google 係唔Index (你諗吓點解)<br />\n用舊版Wordpress，全世界用緊 5.x ，佢仲用緊 4.9.x，因為好多backdoor要依賴舊版Wordpress嘅bug，呢啲都係十分之中國特色嘅玩法<br />\n排版十分之老土，特別字體，有陣明報嘅娘味，一睇就知係大榴槤啲朋友<br />\n佢哋啲page嘅link，得個冧把，因為佢哋明顯方便當中自己管理，無做過SEO，正常嘅website係基本會做番好個permalink啩(雖然香港好多IT人都無做)<br />\n所以我奉勸各位，唔好再share呢啲狗屎垃圾，一啲好處都無。我順便列出一啲，常見嘅狗屎website domain，大家見到可以ignore咗佢，唔好煩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news-lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews-lihkg.com&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=3c494226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news-lihkg.com</a> (明係扮連登)<br />\n<a href=\"http://backup-lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbackup-lihkg.com&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=acbc2166\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">backup-lihkg.com</a> (都係明扮連登)<br />\nbuzznews.news (佢哋好鍾意濫用 .news 嘅domain)<br />\n<a href=\"http://duckhk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fduckhk.com&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e6d271ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">duckhk.com</a> (另一個狗唔搭八domain)<br />\n<br />\n當然，佢哋後面個真Server你見唔到，呢啲賊你只能夠係唔好share，我一向share嘢係十分之謹慎，因為太多人搞 內容農場 ，亦太多製造流量嘅假人，好多Google嘅廣告商啲錢，就俾呢啲公司呃鬼咗。總之大家日後share嘢果陣睇清楚，但Telegram啲人醒好多，中招多數喺WhatsApp同Facebook呢啲相對老化嘅工具上面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/29134/%e5%85%a7%e5%ae%b9%e8%be%b2%e5%a0%b4-%e4%b9%98%e5%8b%a2%e4%bd%9c%e6%83%a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F29134%2F%25e5%2585%25a7%25e5%25ae%25b9%25e8%25be%25b2%25e5%25a0%25b4-%25e4%25b9%2598%25e5%258b%25a2%25e4%25bd%259c%25e6%2583%25a1&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=be3ce538\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/29134/%e5%85%a7%e5%ae%b9%e8%be%b2%e5%a0%b4-%e4%b9%98%e5%8b%a2%e4%bd%9c%e6%83%a1</a>"},{"pid":"4b4c362c4da2aba2b58990ada3c8d2d690dc534c","tid":1638143,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3966dda137150728d791d7ea1a34bb8760adf91c","tid":1638143,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be747aed48b19404c452f88cf75f4099ec4aa5c2","tid":1638143,"uid":3,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"<em>&bull; 本討論區域名只有 <a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a> 及 <a href=\"http://lih.kg\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg</a>，並沒有其他或後備的網站<br />\n&bull; 我們無參與開發其他討論平台或界面相似的網站</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aihJpdV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aihJpdV</a>"},{"pid":"a18ac5916702f47ff069818c8c1afcd7aae5c597","tid":1638143,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3a8cb5373416ccc65305f28f4dcc4d